        <item>
          <actionDate>2017-03-02</actionDate>
          <actionDesc>Introduced in Senate</actionDesc>
          <text><![CDATA[<p>This bill requires the Federal Energy Regulatory Commission, upon request, to reinstate the construction license for the Clark Canyon Dam Hydroelectric Project located on the Beaverhead River in Beaverhead County, Montana.</p> <p>Construction on the project must commence within three years.</p>]]></text>
